188
00:12:44,910 --> 00:12:46,000
I like his lips.

189
00:12:48,140 --> 00:12:49,290
I like his lips.

190
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:54,600
Full lips make for a good kisser, huh?

191
00:12:59,830 --> 00:13:01,130
